{"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore25AccessibilityHeadingLevelO","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"enum","roleHeading":"Enumeration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AccessibilityHeadingLevel"}],"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false},{"name":"macOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"10.15","unavailable":false},{"name":"tvOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false},{"name":"visionOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false},{"name":"watchOS","beta":false,"deprecated":false,"introducedAt":"6.0","unavailable":false}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AccessibilityHeadingLevel"}],"title":"AccessibilityHeadingLevel","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/View\/Text\/Accessibility\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel.swift#L25","fileName":"AccessibilityHeadingLevel.swift"}},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The hierarchy of a heading in relation other headings."}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h1","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h2","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h3","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h4","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h5","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h6","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/unspecified"],"generated":true,"title":"Enumeration Cases","anchor":"Enumeration-Cases"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/init(rawValue:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/s15BitwiseCopyableP","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/SQ","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/SH","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/SY","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/s8SendableP"],"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@frozen","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AccessibilityHeadingLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Assistive technologies can use this to improve a users navigation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"through multiple headings. When users navigate through top level"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"headings they expect the content for each heading to be unrelated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For example, you can categorize a list of available products into sections,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"like Fruits and Vegetables. With only top level headings, this list requires no","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"heading hierarchy, and you use the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/unspecified","type":"reference"},{"text":" heading level. On the other hand, if sections","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"contain subsections, like if the Fruits section has subsections for varieties of Apples,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Pears, and so on, you apply the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h1","type":"reference"},{"text":" level to Fruits and Vegetables, and the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h2","type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level to Apples and Pears.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Except for "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h1","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", be sure to precede all leveled headings by another heading with a level"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that’s one less."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/accessibilityheadinglevel"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/AccessibilityHeadingLevel/h3":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/accessibilityheadinglevel\/h3","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Level 3 heading.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"h3","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"AccessibilityHeadingLevel.h3","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AccessibilityHeadingLevel\/h3"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/SH":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/SH","title":"Swift.Hashable"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/AccessibilityHeadingLevel/h1":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/accessibilityheadinglevel\/h1","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Level 1 heading."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text